# 301-redirect share-preview paths to the backend so WhatsApp/Telegram/iMessage
# follow the redirect at scrape time, land on api.futpools.com/c/:code, and
# read the og.js meta tags + fixture-card image. The shared link text stays
# branded as futpools.com/c/CODE in chat messages. `200!` rewrite would be
# nicer (URL stays branded after click) but Render Static Sites silently
# ignores external destinations on 200 rewrites — only 3xx redirects to
# external URLs are honored.
/c/*    https://api.futpools.com/c/:splat   301
/p/*    https://api.futpools.com/p/:splat   301

# SPA fallback for any other path the React Router needs to handle.
/*      /index.html   200
